      "id": 1,
      "text": "Grandyle Village grew from a 20th‑century suburban boom after the 1935 bridges linked Grand Island to Buffalo.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        24
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
